pageContext.claim: “Here I am at a hangar in Minnesota with 15 or 20 or 25,000 people, and thousands of people that couldn't get in.”
pageContext.analysis: Attendance was much lower at this Bemidji, Minn., rally -- closer to 3,000, according to local reports. No one was turned away for lack of space. Nine people were hospitalized and one died from covid-19 after the rally, according to state health authorities.
